  "texts": [
    "In order to finalize the sample, the study used only the papers that were totally based on ChatGPT, AI and Generative AI tools in educational contexts.",
    "Inclusion and exclusion criteriaThe study used the clear criteria for which studies to include or exclude based on relevance, publication date, type of publication, etc.",
    "For instance, only articles after 2020 were considered to ensure the latest perspectives on ChatGPT in academic settings.",
    "This often involves a two-step process:• Title and abstract screening: Eliminate irrelevant articles from their title and abstract.• Full-text screening: Read the full texts of the shortlisted articles to ensure they are pertinent to the research question.",
    "Data extractionOnce the final list of literature is decided, extract relevant data from each study."
  ]
}